<Head title="Beta Testing Guidelines" description="View our guidelines to become a beta tester." author="Alex Toucan" />
<div id="page">
	<Navbar />
	<main id="guidelines" class="container">
		<h1 class="title">Beta Testing Guidelines</h1>
		<h5> Last Updated: <time>March 12th, 2023</time>. </h5>
		<h5> Into Effect: <time>March 12th, 2023</time>. </h5>
		<div id="disclaimer">
			<p class="my-3">
				<i>This legal document does not apply to the <a href="https:/atproducts.xyz">main website's</a> viewers/users, only the Department of Beta Testing.</i>
			</p>
		</div>
		<div id="definitions">
			<h3> Definitions </h3>
      <p> Department: Department of Beta Testing (DoBT) of AT Products LLC. <br>
      <br> Main Website/General Website: <a href="https://atproducts.xyz">atproducts.xyz</a> <br>
			<br> Company: The Collection of the ATP Database, AT Products, The Script Community, Ethical Hacking Society, CodingHome, and Noodle Hackerspace. <br> Products: Flash Documentation, MDickie Projects, and SMS Bomb. (commonly referred to as "We", "Us", and "Our") <br>
